defs.name: CompilerErrorKind
defs.value:
pub enum CompilerErrorKind {
    VarRedefinition,
    FuncRedefinition,
    TypeRedefinition,
    NoImplicitAny,
    IncompatibleTypes,
    VarUndefined,
    TypeUndefined,
    FuncUndefined,
    ImmutableAssign,
    NoCallSignatures,
    NoProperty,
    MissingParameters,
    ExpectedBooleanExpr,
}
